          "content": "**各位用户：**\n\n根据此前发票政策调整，现做最后提醒：\n\n* **5月份大陆发票补开截止时间为 6月15日 23:59（明天晚23:59）**。逾期后平台将不再受理任何补开请求，请需要开票的用户务必在此之前登录个人中心完成申请。\n* **6月起发票政策调整：**个人支付仅支持开具海外 invoice，不再支持大陆发票；企业对公支付可正常申请大陆发票。\n* **7月1日起**，平台将正式关闭发票管理功能。\n\n感谢大家的理解与支持！\n\n**PackyAPI 团队**\n*2026 年 6 月 14 日*",
          "content_en": "Notice to All Users\n\nFollowing the previous adjustment to our invoicing policy, we are issuing this final reminder:\n\n• Deadline for reissuing May mainland China invoices: 23:59 on June 15 (tomorrow). No reissuance requests will be accepted by our platform past this deadline. Users requiring invoices must submit applications via the Personal Center before the cutoff time.\n\n• Revised invoicing policy effective June 1: Personal payments will only be issued overseas invoices; mainland China invoices will no longer be available for personal orders. Corporate payments via official corporate accounts may still apply for mainland China invoices as usual.\n\n• Starting July 1, the dedicated invoice management feature on the platform will be permanently shut down.\n\nThank you for your understanding and support.\n\nPackyAPI Team\nJune 14, 2026",
