          "category": "group",
          "content": "【公告】Codex 分组维护状态通知\n\n为了进一步提升服务稳定性与整体性能，Codex 分组目前处于维护状态。\n\n当前状态：\nCodex 分组正在进行系统维护与优化升级，预计于周一恢复正常运行。\n\n维护期间影响：\n维护期间可能出现断连、高延迟、响应超时、服务不可用等现象，相关功能体验可能受到影响。\n\n建议措施：\n维护期间建议使用 ClaudeCode，并选择 Claude-Sale 分组。目前 Claude-Sale 分组执行 1.5X 倍率计费。\n\n后续进展：\n我们将持续推进维护工作，并在恢复后第一时间同步相关通知。\n\n感谢各位用户的理解与支持。如有任何问题，欢迎随时联系我们。\n\nPackyAPI 团队\n2026 年 6 月 12 日",
          "content_en": "[Announcement] Codex Group Maintenance Status Notice\n\nTo further improve service stability and overall performance, the Codex group is currently under maintenance.\n\nCurrent Status:\nThe Codex group is undergoing system maintenance and optimization upgrades, and is expected to return to normal operation on Monday.\n\nImpact During Maintenance:\nDuring the maintenance period, issues such as disconnections, high latency, response timeouts, and service unavailability may occur, and the user experience of related features may be affected.\n\nRecommended Action:\nDuring maintenance, we recommend using ClaudeCode and selecting the Claude-Sale group. The Claude-Sale group is currently billed at 1.5X the normal rate.\n\nFollow-up Progress:\nWe will continue to carry out the maintenance work and share the relevant notice as soon as service is restored.\n\nThank you for your understanding and support. If you have any questions, please feel free to contact us at any time.\n\nPackyAPI Team\nJune 12, 2026",
          "content_en_src": "4728598644f28363",
          "extra": "",
          "id": 18,
          "publishDate": "2026-06-12T04:31:58.922Z",
          "type": "default"
        },
        {
          "content": "【运营调整】\n当前我们的开票类型有：海外invoice、大陆发票\n因运营策略调整：\n6月份开始，所有新购个人支付将无法开具大陆发票，只支持海外invoice\n6月份开始，只支持企业对公支付开具大陆发票\n所有用户5月份的支付订单仍能在6月份补开大陆发票，截止至6月15号\n——PackyTeam",
          "content_en": "[Operational Adjustment]\nOur current invoicing types are: overseas invoice and Mainland China invoice.\n\nDue to an adjustment in our operational strategy:\nStarting in June, all newly purchased individual payments will no longer be eligible for Mainland China invoices; only overseas invoices will be supported.\nStarting in June, Mainland China invoices will only be available for corporate bank-to-bank payments.\nAll users’ payment orders from May can still be reissued with Mainland China invoices in June, with the deadline being June 15.\n— PackyTeam",
          "content_en_src": "25153937a6680753",
          "extra": "",
          "id": 17,
          "publishDate": "2026-05-21T11:33:07.922Z",
          "type": "default"
        },
        {
          "content": "【公告】新增异常缓存补偿机制\n\n为了进一步提升服务稳定性和用户体验，我们上线了异常缓存补偿机制。\n\n补偿规则：\n当系统检测到连续创建异常缓存时，将对该部分异常缓存产生的费用只收取原费用 20% 的扣费。\n\n当前生效范围：\n目前仅在 Claude 渠道 开启 Beta 测试。\n\n后续计划：\n该机制将逐步覆盖 PackyAPI 全部渠道。\n此机制主要用于减少高峰期因异常缓存导致的不必要扣费情况，保护用户利益。\n感谢各位用户一直以来的支持与反馈。如在使用过程中遇到任何问题，欢迎随时联系我们。\n\nPackyAPI 团队\n2026 年 5 月",
          "content_en": "[Announcement] New Exception Cache Compensation Mechanism\n\nTo further improve service stability and user experience, we have launched an exception cache compensation mechanism.\n\nCompensation rules:\nWhen the system detects consecutive abnormal cache creations, only 20% of the original fee will be charged for the fees generated by those abnormal caches.\n\nCurrent scope:\nAt present, it is only enabled for Beta testing on the Claude channel.\n\nFuture plans:\nThis mechanism will be gradually expanded to all PackyAPI channels.\nIt is mainly intended to reduce unnecessary charges caused by abnormal caches during peak periods and protect users’ interests.\nThank you all for your continued support and feedback. If you encounter any issues while using the service, please feel free to contact us at any time.\n\nPackyAPI Team\nMay 2026",
          "content_en_src": "de8377c42741ad78",
          "extra": "",
          "id": 16,
          "publishDate": "2026-05-11T11:33:12.926Z",
          "type": "default"
        },
        {
          "content": "【重要公告】Claude价格与服务调整通知\n近期受 A 社封控策略和额度降低造成的成本影响，服务可用性有所下降。为保障使用的稳定与连续性，我们将于 2026年 4 月 1 日12:00起，暂时将 CC 分组倍率由 1.5 上调至 2.5。\n我们将持续关注封控政策变化——若 A 社进一步加强风控，倍率可能再次涨幅；若情况缓解，我们也将第一时间恢复至 1.5 倍率，以回馈各位长期支持的用户。作为建议，当前可以选择使用 codex 或者 cc-sale 分组。其他分组不受此影响。\n同时我们的退款始终保持开放，售后退款邮箱：xxx。\nPacky 始终以“高可用与稳定服务”为首要目标。对于此次临时调整可能带来的不便，我们深表歉意，并感谢各位的理解与支持！\nPacky Team\n2026 年 3月 30 日",
          "content_en": "[Important Notice] Claude Pricing and Service Adjustment Notice\n\nRecently, due to the cost impact caused by A Inc.’s restrictions and reduced quotas, service availability has declined somewhat. To ensure stable and continuous usage, we will temporarily raise the CC group multiplier from 1.5 to 2.5 starting at 12:00 on April 1, 2026.\n\nWe will continue to monitor changes in the restriction policy — if A Inc. further tightens risk controls, the multiplier may increase again; if the situation eases, we will restore the 1.5x multiplier at the first opportunity to thank our long-term users for their support. As a recommendation, you may currently choose to use the codex or cc-sale groups. Other groups are not affected by this change.\n\nAt the same time, refunds remain available at all times. For after-sales refund inquiries, please email: xxx.\n\nPacky has always made “high availability and stable service” our top priority. We sincerely apologize for any inconvenience this temporary adjustment may cause, and thank you for your understanding and support!\n\nPacky Team  \nMarch 30, 2026",
          "content_en_src": "11355e1737f639d2",
          "extra": "",
